high_descs: Turn left move towards the fridge.
Pick the fruit from the fridge.
Turn left and turn right move towards the sink.
Place the bowl fruit inside the sink, pick the fruit from the sink.
Turn right move towards the fridge.
Place the fruit inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To place the fruit inside the fridge.

high_descs: Move forward, turn left and move forward again to the fridge.
Open the door, take out the mango and close the door.
Turn left, move forward, and turn right to the sink.
Place a mango in the sink, tap the water to clean it, and take it out from the sink.
Turn around to the right, turn left, move forward, turn left again to the fridge.
Open the door, place a mango in the fridge, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned mango in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and turn left and then head straight towards the fridge.
Pick up mango from the fridge.
Go left and head straight towards the wall. After that, turn left and walk straight into the room, turning to the sink on your right.
Turn around and turn left and then head straight towards the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Washing mango and placing it back on fridge
